This project IMPLEMENTS and BUILDS ON the following prior work. We are grateful
to these authors; this software does not include their code or any trained
model weights.

METHOD — Covariant obfuscation
  "Towards Privacy-Preserving LLM Inference via Covariant Obfuscation"
  Yu Lin, Qizhi Zhang, Wenqiang Ruan, Daode Zhang, Jue Hong, Ye Wu, Hanning Xia,
  Yunlong Mao, Sheng Zhong (2026). arXiv:2603.01499  ("AloePri")
  -> The covariant rotation P that this project applies to the weights is their
     contribution. This is an independent implementation of the published method.

DISTRIBUTION SUBSTRATE — inspiration
  Leyten's "shard" distributed-inference engine. https://github.com/leyten/shard
  -> The layer-sharding / verifiable-receipt approach informed the mesh design.
     No shard code is included here; this is an independent implementation.

